{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 1}, 'user_id': 'guyzph02jqMCmiqxoDQ3hg', 'review_id': 'TsdoOYzUBsm3HOViAgX1Bw', 'text': 'Great COBB salad, lamb burger was alright but nothing great.', 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 3, 'date': '2013-06-30', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 1, 'cool': 3}, 'user_id': 'wFORsmMSyixtjTINIv1zyg', 'review_id': 'bEc0bLr9C2c9ZvE0lAoe5w', 'text': "I've been to CPH 3 times now and will definitely be back again. The scallop dish Is a must as is the short ribs. My dining partner ordered the yellow tail special which was excellent. Lets face it, you can get scallops and short ribs at a lot of restaurants  but not of this quality and price, most dish's are $20 to $25. What CPH does is deliver consistently high quality food at great value, add in the good service and friendly staff and you don't have to wonder why this has become a local favorite.\nI'd be remiss if I didn't give a shout out to the bar manager and mixologist Tom, his craft cocktails are a great, I'm a fan of the Boulvardier.", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 4, 'date': '2013-07-01', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'Qe2WAZmEzRkEMHScI7l4uA', 'review_id': 'loq98lrmEDpOVVK94D0jqg', 'text': 'Best drinks for your money in town if you like whiskey and gin.', 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2013-07-03', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 1}, 'user_id': 'nCaR5m3nnenrDnpypip3Sw', 'review_id': '-Y5SvD8Zztxy87_kDB76iA', 'text': "The atmosphere is quite fun with energy and great for couples and groups. Moderate level of noise. Simple but nice design. Great area for walking around Old Town! I ordered the Sangria, which is house made and it was quite good but a bit sweet for my liking. The scallops were from Maine and the entire dish was enjoyable but scallops were more gritty than normal (I love scallops). The purred grits that they are served over top of was very tasty and it will give you a cream fix for those who don't, or can't eat cream based sauces. I can't usually do desert but I was able to love and tolerate the flour-less, gluten free chocolate mint cake. It was more like a fudge but way lighter! I also had a a nice glass of ice wine from Canada (the best area by far for ice wine) and it was perfect!  The waitress (Cat) was very very sweet and pleasantly knowledgable about the menu. Perfect for this type of Restaurant, while attentive and happy! This is a fine stop in Scottsdale.", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 4, 'date': '2013-07-12', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 2, 'cool': 3}, 'user_id': 'cUjy7cqOxoqq5l7XrNx4BA', 'review_id': 'zzjY7BavMGEqqzUrmceuDA', 'text': "I couldn't wait to try this place. All the reviews and word of mouth were so positive that I felt that I was going in for an awesome experience. Well, I was somewhat let down. Despite the restaurant's success and  I am happy for them,  I found it impossible to carry a conversation with my friend without constantly having the repeat myself....and that just got old real quick.\n\nAs we sat down, I already knew I wanted out. The food was okay...definitely not blown away. I had the lamb sandwich as I wanted something that hopefully would not take long to make and minimize my time...so bottomline, what could have been a great experience simply wasn't...and the noise was just unbearable and exhausting. Gastropub maybe, just not the place for me....definitely not a romantic joint....\n\nMy friend had the steak salad, and all there was were greens and meat...no other veggies ...just thought t looked kinda bland and boring.", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 3, 'date': '2013-07-14', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 1, 'cool': 1}, 'user_id': 'aM72jFxgmCII32qUZS6CWw', 'review_id': 'rgROJ7jPo7TtnW7r8xaiwQ', 'text': 'i tried the chowder that tasted like a ingredients simply dumped in water and served.', 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 2, 'date': '2013-07-14', 'type': 'review'}
