{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'jWpbwcHxQtggzIISVmDGvg', 'review_id': 'nqX8coyCcj-uInMpWVHaLw', 'text': 'The chopped salad gets 5 stars, but the entrees get 3 stars, which puts me at an overall rating of 4. I had the scallops and grits...they were very flavorful, but a little too heavy on the oil.  Husband had meatloaf and said it was average.  We both loved the chopped salad though.  I wish it was a littlebit larger because I would be perfectly happy eating it as my entree.', 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 4, 'date': '2014-01-04', 'type': 'review'}
