{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 1, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'pgWFqsnLh4-yKc0-aVzzlg', 'review_id': '0W5xqrEegA1XzBMH5idWWw', 'text': "Best cocktails and service in Scottsdale!!  I am never disappointed when I go to Citizen Public House.  The cocktails are unique and delicious (ask Thomas to make them for you, he's amazing), and the service is impeccable.  For dinner ask to sit in Sam's section; he is by far one of the most knowledgeable, on-point servers I have ever had.  All of his recommendations have always been phenomenal and he has a cadence about him that makes you feel like he is enjoying the dining experience as much as you are.\n\nFood standouts: Chopped Salad; Scallops; and the Tenderloin Wrap\nDrink standout: Manhattan; trust me on this one, it's out of this world.", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2014-10-02', 'type': 'review'}
