{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'SHieHKBOvlu4f8LBQVdcvg', 'review_id': '9yMv2W2O31Pa9Ay98AoOLw', 'text': "Omg! My daughter heard about this place and we decided to check it out on one of my trips to Phoenix. We shared the piggy and waffle, and the Cobb salad. It was enough food for the two of us would even know my stomach was portruding, I could have kept eating another round of both! Since then I've been trying to make chicken and pancakes so I could get that combination of syrup and meats! Can't wait to go back and see what they have on the menu next. And by the way, the Cobb salad was really unusual it had chopped smoked salmon pieces. It was fabulous!!", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2014-10-11', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'NT8pR2F04s7EQT1pIQ7-Fw', 'review_id': '4ehDaN6jNjmvp16Io1z2Dw', 'text': 'At the end of long day of golf and fun we looked this place up on Yelp and saw the rating. It didn\'t disappoint. Josh was a top 10 waiter and the food was all amazing. They also hooked up our 10 year old with a "kid\'s meal" modified from what they served. I should add that the hand crafted gin and tequila cocktails were amazing!!! It was the perfect last meal of a great vacation.', 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2014-10-13', 'type': 'review'}
