{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': '3y9dRQgLorf9c4yAJZ7A0Q', 'review_id': 'aWTWShRNi67K4vOi8DdsVQ', 'text': 'The wait staff was very helpful. The seasonal mule was delicious. The food was okay although one of our orders never came. However the room is very noisy. A difficult place for a conversation.  Would not recommend for a meal over which you intend to have a good conversation.', 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 3, 'date': '2015-03-23', 'type': 'review'}
