{'votes': {'funny': 1, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'C-kkL06MZ5Gt9B9msf-DmQ', 'review_id': 'acAsArgLUEQ1_3eidUMYRA', 'text': "For our first time here, it was a pretty good experience. Tip: make reservations or get there early. Saturday night we got there around 6:30 & the only seating was around the bar. Thank God there were four open seats. We ordered a few drinks. Not the best we've had that day (considering we started at the Second Story Liquor Bar...BOOM) but we had food & drinks. I ordered the pork belly pastrami. That LITTLE plate of food was AWESOME! Flavor packed & delicious. The next time we'll make reservations so we can sit on that awesome patio!", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 4, 'date': '2015-04-23', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 1, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'oau8IjRcoDz7801bq5ehew', 'review_id': '0IFUpi9-MBCxjK6uRoyXRA', 'text': 'One word...awesome!  We started off with the crab cakes; they were very good and so was the bed of slaw they were served over.  The chopped salad is like no other chopped salad I have had before, yum!  The service was spot on.  Citizen Public House does everything right!', 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2015-04-23', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 1, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'xF5i2z08mqTObEcDXe23eQ', 'review_id': '6WPzNzaTaron2OnpJPnQcA', 'text': 'We went a Friday night with my family of three kids. The kids had the Nush fries with the dip and it was gone in seconds. They also had the linguine spinach pasta so tasty!\nI had the rosted vegetable salad with the dressing that was perfect my husband  had the chicken kabob that they were tender and delicious.\nService was friendly and so helpful with menu suggestions! \nAs a family with kids is hard to find a restaurant to please all the taste buds but Nush knocks it out off the park!', 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2015-04-25', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'tSDEjyvRTW1pIUML31j7HA', 'review_id': 'f3GlkCaUJ2mpFE2t22skmg', 'text': "Came here for dinner, make a reservation it gets packed, especially on the weekends. It's in the heart of old town, great location, big open windows with the bar in the middle, the ambience was great. Very noisy though, so don't think it's something intimate. You HAVE TO order the original chopped salad, the most amazing salad I've ever had. They put dried corn in the salad and it tastes like crouton but sweet, and the smoked salmon for protein, the flavors are amazing. The pork belly pastrami was good, but nothing special. It tastes just like any other pork belly dish but it was still cooked perfectly. The porcini fillet mignon was really delicious, the rub was very tasty and the steak was cooked perfectly to my liking. They have a great wine list and specialty cocktails. Great place to hang out with a small group and the people there are nice and knowledgeable. Will definitely be back.", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2015-04-26', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'i4PMmVTdLFxAqPRdUlMHHQ', 'review_id': 'nacmDwLi74FUxa1h3YDMyA', 'text': "Great food as always! I've never reviewed CPH on Yelp and have finally got around to it. Had dinner here this past weekend and overall service and food was excellent. I have found that some Scottsdale restaurants can sometimes have some stuffy/uppity type of service (I'm better than you vibe at times.) Not the case here! Everyone is always so friendly and accommodating and they aim to please. Saturday was super busy and a packed restaurant - food quality or presentation didn't suffer at all because of it and neither did the service. Highly recommend the fondue starter and osso bucco. I would however like to see a couple more Pinot Grigio and Sauvignon Blanc options on the white wine by glass menu. All in all it doesn't matter! All around great. Keep it up, CPH! I will continue to frequent when I'm in Scottsdale.", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2015-04-27', 'type': 'review'}
