{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 2, 'cool': 2}, 'user_id': 'KbhBJXXqK8FOwwF4Nr9iUQ', 'review_id': 'blXgnZXizSijAKXInIBSyA', 'text': "I really can't add much more than all of the previous reviews. The service was great! The food didn't disappoint and I'm absolutely stuffed. \n\nOur table of 5 consumed:\n\nCatfish Appetizer\nRosemary Nuts\nChopped Salad x 2\nButtermilk Chicken x 2\nPork Osso Buco x 2 \nSome cocktails (I had lemonade)\n\nI substituted mashed potatoes for the succotash on the chicken entree and it was delicious. The chopped salad was yummy as well but smaller than how the waiter described it. \n\nThat's all. Going into a food coma now.", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2015-06-24', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': '3hxrCoQUUqdjduAqpRveNw', 'review_id': 'r1IVxOG1R1isV7kPE6ph9A', 'text': "We went to this restaurant with another couple. It happened to be my birthday the next day. The service was superb. \nHave you ever had pickled okra? It's very good. \nThe chopped salad was light and refreshing. \nWhen in doubt go with the chicken. I'm glad I did. The chicken was flavorful and comforting. Others at my table had the tuna and the braised beef. \nI was so satisfied I had no intention of having dessert. But they brought out a chocolate brownie with ice cream and a candle. How can I refuse that? The waiter was smooth, and surprised me!!  \nThank you for a wonderful dinner. I'm definitely going back.", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2015-06-27', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 1, 'cool': 2}, 'user_id': 'b5NysWHPHvhd0EA6-yCRCQ', 'review_id': 'gytFNZMkFXEwESwAY6mkLA', 'text': '100/5 yessss 100/5.\nBeen to many restaurants in this area and best overall experience I have EVER had! I usually will substitute good food for bad service but this place had both. \n\nWent to happy hour first for a great happy hour! Their cocktails were great and only 5 dollars! Michael the bartender was amazing! Free samples and since it was me and my girlfriends first time there he ordered us their famous chopped salad on him! The dinner and server was also great ! Definitely recommend this place to anyone looking for awesome food, fantastic service, and ambiance!', 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2015-06-27', 'type': 'review'}
