{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'Yf6grptUf_MXNU_XeNLtxA', 'review_id': 'u7_fppInRJGV5qj-eu4fZg', 'text': "I am always excited for dinner at the CPH! I am sure every review says it, but seriously, order the chopped salad. I've been here several times and I always get the salad and then try something else from the menu. Nearly everything has been delicious, especially the chia seared tuna. My boyfriend had the crab cakes last time we were here, and I recall them being a bit of a miss. \nThe drink menu has something for everyone from cocktails and beer to a complete wine list. \n\nGreat place for a date night or dinner with friends. Although I will caution, when the place is full, it can be very loud and hard to hear.", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 4, 'date': '2015-07-22', 'type': 'review'}
