{'votes': {'funny': 1, 'useful': 1, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': '5mqDpUiqKBePIC9UZ2G5Dw', 'review_id': 'y8w1OJrF8F7gjTIeduZT_A', 'text': "Good place. I definitely came in with extremely high expectations, given the rave reviews this place has. The food was definitely good. I ordered the steak with asparagus which i thought was really dry. My sister had the sea bass which was good. Chopped salad was good as well. Crab cakes were meh. I feel like there are better restaurants around. I'd definitely be back, but I wouldn't give this place 5 stars. \n\nService was very good, atmosphere was perfect for dates.", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 4, 'date': '2015-08-12', 'type': 'review'}
