{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'xjXPntJcY85k2PbokD6BVQ', 'review_id': 'kznc7tDrSX5kiLlzKb2ypg', 'text': "Great concept, definitely one of Arizona's best restaurants. The handcrafted drinks hit hard and are delivered in style. They have a beautiful private upstairs for parties. The food really works here. It is a dedicated chef driven restaurant, so quality is all they send you from that kitchen. Some personal favorites are the Pork Belly Pastrami, Flat Iron Steak, Scallops, and Burrata. I recommend this spot for anyone in Scottsdale.", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2015-08-20', 'type': 'review'}
{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 1}, 'user_id': 'fzi7nGcFOuNlhVkbDaFlAg', 'review_id': 'gYVa14dvq7K7G68zIR_-5A', 'text': "If there is a place that deserves more then 5 stars this is it!  My wife and I stopped here for a cocktail and appetizer. It was a Monday right when they opened at 2:00 pm so it would have been easy to expect poor service. Absolutely not the case. \n\nIn all my years I've never met a more knowledgable bartender. He is very committed to his craft and provided great information about the drink choices and the food menu as well. Very easy to talk to, polite and just a great overall guy. \n\nI had a craft beer and my wife a glass of wine. My wife is very knowledgeable about wine and the suggestion by the bartender was a perfect fit for her pallet. \n\nMy only regret is that we had already eaten lunch. The bacon popcorn was amazing and I have no doubt the rest of the menu is as well. \n\nWe will be back here again for lunch/dinner and if the same bartender is working I know where we will be sitting. \n\nJust flawless in all aspects. Thanks for a great experience on our date day away from our children.", 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2015-08-20', 'type': 'review'}
