{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 1}, 'user_id': 'tfmqNdm7rsG5LiPYcuOcqg', 'review_id': 'RE39rsq2boKNq5-uWxvXvg', 'text': u'My fianc\xe9 and I were visiting the area and decided to try this restaurant. It was absolutely incredible. We had the scallops and short rib tacos. Scallops are by far the best we have ever had! We also had the fondue and heart of caramel dessert. Both were also incredible. The heart of caramel was a perfect combination of rich chocolate with refreshing white chocolate ice cream. The salted caramel splash on the plate just pulled it all together. The wait staff was so polite and friendly. Our water glasses were never empty and they spent time with us to recommend places in the city to check out. We will always remember this night!', 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 5, 'date': '2015-08-24', 'type': 'review'}
