{'votes': {'funny': 0, 'useful': 0, 'cool': 0}, 'user_id': 'JcHoxYvE9ljII8Yvg00TNw', 'review_id': '4NsHrZilJYfOqO3Z2DzCIQ', 'text': u'We went with a group of 8 on a Friday night and had a reservation. We were sat promptly and on time. The drinks were tasty but small pours for the price. The chopped salad was delicious. The entr\xe9es were average to small portions. I had the short ribs which were dry. The greens were undercooked and extremely bitter. My wife had the meatloaf which was also very dry.  \n\nThe kicker to the evening was when we asked out waiter James to split the checks. His reply was rude and condescending but did eventually split the checks. Overall it was ok but not a place I would go back to.', 'business_id': 'MuIXnv7Oq7X3-4aEsp9dDA', 'stars': 2, 'date': '2015-10-31', 'type': 'review'}
